# Mobile Rules
- Expo SDK 51 + Expo Router v3 for navigation.
- Animations: Reanimated 2 worklets only. 60 FPS target.
- Lists: FlashList, never FlatList.
- Images: expo-image with caching. Compress before upload (max 2MB).
- State: TanStack Query (server), Zustand (client).
- Tokens: expo-secure-store. Never AsyncStorage for secrets.
- Touch targets: minimum 44px.
- All strings through @trendywheels/i18n.
